1.3.022702
==========================================================================================
Fix errors starting cyrus-imap:
When cyrus-imapd failed to start or is take many long time to start, Artica will try to repair the database, depends of the database size,
the repair operation could be aborted and corrupt cyrus databases.
In this version, artica will not try to start coverage operations.

Adding more tools to repair cyrus in cyrus-imap section.(see http://www.artica.fr/index.php?ID=1881)

Adding features to centralize white lists and black list in artica around spamassassin, amavisd and Kaspersky Anti-spam. (see http://www.artica.fr/index.php?ID=1882)
Improve function for starting clamd: To prevent corrupted configuration file, artica write the entire file of clamd.conf.

