Change support of RoundCube parameters engine.
   When you save RoundCube settings, Parameters are directly stored on disk instead using the LDAP database server.
    This in order to prevent corrupted datas or errors in LDAP.
    With this version it sould be normal if your last settings are not saved in the configuration file cause this change.
    (see http://www.artica.fr/forum/viewtopic.php?f=40&t=876)
    
