Fix MAJOR BUG
A function in charge of finding processes return PID numbers.
in 1.3 version, if a process is not found this function report -1 has PID number
But when artica whant to kill a process that didn't exists, this function return -1 (a kill -9 -1 disturb the system).
All Artica upgraded from 1.2 to 1.3 are encouraged to update to this release.
(see http://www.artica.fr/forum/viewtopic.php?f=25&t=866)

